data.description:
The house is 5 years old in like new condition. Corner lot, additional off-street parking. 
Good location, in city limits, near by schools and stores, fast and easy access to the freeway. Only 15 minutes from the PDX airport. 

For additional questions:
text or email only

For a potential tenant:
1. Background and credit check is required. 
2. Tenant is responsible for all the utilities. 
Gas/electricity/water/trash/phone/cable/internet 
3. Tenant needs to take care of the lawn/ mow grass. 
4. First month, last month & deposit is required
